(n+1)P_{n+1} (x)-xP_{n+1}^{'} = x(nP_{n}(x)-xP_{n}^{'}(x))-P_{n-1}
(n+1)P_{n+1}(x)=(2n+1)xP_{n}-nP_{n-1}(x) \tag 1
 P_{n+1}^{'}-P_{n-1}^{'}=(2n+1)P_{n}
(n+1)P_{n+1}(x)=xP_{n+1}^{'}-xP_{n-1}^{'}-nP_{n-1}(x)
P_{n}^{'} =xP_{n-1}^{'}+nP_{n-1}
(n+1)P_{n+1}(x)-xP_{n+1}^{'}=x(nP_{n-1}(x)-xP_{n}^{'}(x))-nP_{n-1}(x)
